post_description: Some AI news: we're moving PyTorch, the open source AI framework led by Meta researchers, to become a project governed under the Linux Foundation.   PyTorch has become one of the leading AI platforms with more than 150,000 projects on GitHub built on the framework.   The new PyTorch Foundation board will include many of the AI leaders who've helped get the community where it is today, including Meta and our partners at AMD, Amazon, Google, Microsoft, and Nvidia.   I'm excited to keep building the PyTorch community and advancing AI research.
